      },
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the hemolysis scalar transport equation on three systematically refined hexahedral meshes. Observed spatial order of accuracy of 1.93 (formal: 2nd order) confirms correct implementation of discretisation scheme. Code verification criterion satisfied."
