      "rationale": "Validation experiments were performed on the identical FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry used in the COU assessment. Operating conditions overlap the COU envelope at all 5 assessment points. Fluid analogue properties are within specified tolerances. Similarity index assessed at 0.85/1.0. Relevance criterion satisfied."
    },
    {
