      "rationale": "At MRL 2 for a commercially certified solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2), separate numerical solver error assessment beyond code verification and discretization error is not required. Solver iterative convergence is monitored via residual drop of 6 orders of magnitude and mass imbalance < 0.01%; no solver-level defects identified. Factor scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2."
    },
    {
