      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. The analysis team holds documented CFD competency qualifications and the simulation workflow is governed by a written simulation plan reviewed by an independent credibility assessor. No evidence of user-induced errors identified during peer review. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2."
    },
    {
