      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample variability assessment is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is a standardised reference geometry; device-to-device manufacturing variability is not applicable to this reference geometry study. Blood analogue fluid was prepared from a single batch with certified composition. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2."
